svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104boh1719653049340.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/boh1719653049340.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/boh1719653049340.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dlb1665702523603\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $exp10\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dlb1665702523603___exp_262387\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the base 10 exponential of X (10<sup class=\"ph sup\">X</sup>). </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__topic_d82733e1_d82734e1_d82735e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__p_d82736e1_d82737e1_d82738e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$exp10</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__topic_d54617e1_d54618e1_d54619e1_d54620e1_d54621e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100342e78\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1__entry__3\">\n Numeric constant from -9999 through +9999, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a numeric value.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__topic_d54622e1_d54623e1_d54624e1_d54625e1_d54626e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100342e132\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__p_d82745e1_d82746e1_d82747e1\">Base 10 exponential of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> (10 raised to the power <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__p_d82748e1_d82749e1_d82750e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$exp</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$exp10</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> -1207</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNDERFLOW&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Underflow. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> -1208 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_OVERFLOW&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dlb1665702523603__table_d8444e1_d8445e1_d8446e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Overflow. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__topic_d54627e1_d54628e1_d54629e1_d54630e1_d54631e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100342e243\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__topic_d54632e1_d54633e1_d54634e1_d54635e1_d54636e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1100342e253\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dlb1665702523603__p_d82760e1_d82761e1_d82762e1\">The result of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$exp10</span> must be in the range 10-9999 through 109999, which means that <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> must be in the range -9999 through +9999.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdn1665702523449.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$log10</a><p>Return the base 10 logarithm of X (log10X).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419756\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419756\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$exp10 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $exp10 Return the base 10 exponential of X (10 X ). $exp10 ( X ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description X Numeric Numeric constant from -9999 through +9999, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a numeric value. Return Values Base 10 exponential of X (10 raised to the power X ). If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $exp and $exp10 Value Error constant Meaning -1207 <UPROCERR_UNDERFLOW> Underflow. -1208 <UPROCERR_OVERFLOW> Overflow. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The result of $exp10 must be in the range 10-9999 through 109999, which means that X must be in the range -9999 through +9999. Related Links $log10 Return the base 10 logarithm of X (log10X). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}